      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">The Coach's Dilemma: AI Can Run Your Frameworks. It Can't Replace What You Actually Do.</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">EOS, Scaling Up, Vistage playbooks are getting automated. The coaches who survive will be the ones who encode what the playbook can't capture.</p>
